      "content": "it's just so hard to get any rest and i'm starting to feel really run down. i'm not looking to make a huge deal out of it, i just want to know if it's actually dangerous or just something doctors say to be extra cautious. like, is there any actual evidence that taking one dose of sudafed is harmful to a baby in the second trimester? i just need to know if i can sleep tonight or if i really have to wait until monday.",
